title: L’addio glamour al Trono di Spade
body:
L’addio glamour al Trono di Spade

Si è tenuta a New York la Premiere dell’ultimo capitolo della saga più acclamata di questo decennio, Il Trono di Spade.

A partire dall’esordio nel 2011, la serie ha proiettato il pubblico in una dimensione magica e medievale, ricca di battaglie coinvolgenti e momenti toccanti che hanno reso i Sette Regni realtà.

Purtroppo questo mondo di fantasia che ha riunito per anni milioni di fan è…

summary:
I will never stop being pissed that Ser Arthur Dayne was 100 times hotter than Rhaegar.
I know it's a petty detail, but much was...
body:
I will never stop being pissed that Ser Arthur Dayne was 100 times hotter than Rhaegar.

I know it’s a petty detail, but much was touted of this man as being the most beautiful man in the seven Kingdoms - jfc, even Viserys was better looking than Rhaegar.

My friends know how much I harp on about it, but seeing I am rewatching I’ll take this opportunity to bitch once again. 🙄

summary: The new Les Miserables and Game of Thrones air at the same time on April 14th.
title: The new Les Miserables and Game of Thrones air at the same time on April 14th.
body: Looks like I’ll have to choose between one sad show about a bunch of people dying when a monarchy fails to successfully take care of the common people, despite years of possible changes for the better reverting back to tyrannic grasps for power by the old regimes, leading to social unrest and personal tragedies for the high and low alike…or another sad show about a bunch of people dying in France.
